name: Russian Attack
description: Conducted assault operations in the Vovchoyarivka - Spirne and Mykolaivka - Spirne directions. Suffered significant losses and withdrew.

name: Russian Attack
column4: Ukrainian soldiers successfully repulsed offensive actions in the direction of Nyrkove - Berestove. Also
